-- India to Finance $178 Million of Water Projects Across Tanzania
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2012-10-04T12:44:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-04/india-to-finance-178-million-of-water-projects-across-tanzania.html
India approved $178 million of
financing through its Export-Import Bank for water supply and
infrastructure projects in Dar es Salaam and Chalinze, the
Tanzania Daily News reported, citing the Indian High Commission.  The India statement said $76 million in credit was also
approved for tractors and agricultural equipment, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
